Package: mnlmixte
Title: Multinomial Logistic Regression for Mixed Data
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    c(
        person(given = "Lansana", family = "CISSE", email = "l.cisse@univ-lyon2.fr", role = c("aut", "cre")),
        person(given = "Pierre", family = "Bourbon", email = "p.bourbon@univ-lyon2.fr", role = "aut")
    )
Description: A package for multinomial logistic regression tailored for mixed datasets 
    (categorical and numerical variables). It supports variable selection, parallel processing 
    for large-scale datasets, and provides tools for model evaluation, prediction, and data preprocessing. 
    The package also includes support for exporting models in PMML format and visualization of feature importance.
